  "title": "feat(css): add devtools for CSS variable config",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\n[FX-3569](https://algolia.atlassian.net/browse/FX-3569)\r\n\r\nThis PR introduces a developer tools panel for InstantSearch CSS that enables real-time configuration and experimentation with CSS variables using [Tweakpane](https://tweakpane.github.io/docs/) library.\r\n\r\nChanges:\r\n- Adds Tweakpane integration for interactive CSS variable configuration\r\n- Implements automatic CSS variable config generation from SCSS source files\r\n- Provides a `createInstantSearchDevtools()` API for embedding the panel\r\n- Provides an inject module for automatic devtools initialization\r\n\r\n**Result**\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1447\" height=\"1257\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/89a3c4e1-7cc0-4290-be53-ccc84d32e657\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[FX-3569]: https://algolia.atlassian.net/browse/FX-3569?atlOrigin=eyJpIjoiNWRkNTljNzYxNjVmNDY3MDlhMDU5Y2ZhYzA5YTRkZjUiLCJwIjoiZ2l0aHViLWNvbS1KU1cifQ",
